{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the two of us survived, and he said, I'm going to take you home, to his home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my fiance was living not very far from him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, well, I'm going to give you a shirt because without a shirt, how can you present yourself?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, easily.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll just walk in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He gave me-- You know, I was so tired, so weak, that while we were waiting for the streetcar to come, I was sitting down on the curb because I just didn't have any strength to wait standing up for the streetcar.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was shaving myself with those safety shaver, this bone on both sides, was sticking out so badly that for a month when I was shaving myself I cut out the skin because it was in the way.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't think I was weighing more than, I would say, about 65, 70 pounds, I was-- all my bones were sticking out, and it has taken me months and months and months before-- You know, on my honeymoon, I had diarrhea, and I couldn't make it to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you like to have a honeymoon like this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long did you stay in Hungary?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were staying there until 1949, April 17, when we have decided that this is not for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were going to Austria through Czechoslovakia, and we had a smuggler who was surprised, who came up to our apartment and said, well, this is a very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have an apartment like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
